      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint${sound:npc_GereintKid_9816_qu_02.ogg}<BR>So Hirendel created a Nest but you defeated him, and a <FONT color=#a82424>Child you’ve never seen before</FONT> suddenly appeared and took him away? And Grele has been like this ever since?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-accepting-acceptted" mid="75" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That’s right… I’m glad you’re back, Geraint. Can you take care of Grele while I look for Shalica?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-" mid="12" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>It was all part of Shalica’s big plan…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-1-a" mid="14" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint${sound:npc_GereintKid_9817_qu_01.ogg}<BR>He probably just lost control of himself after being intimidated by the mysterious Child. Why do I have to trouble myself and take care of him? He’ll just get better after some time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-1-b" mid="16" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Grele is a mutant Child so it can be dangerous when his energy is unstable like this. I won’t take long so please do this for me.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-1-" mid="18" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint${sound:npc_GereintKid_9817_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Hmph, whatever… I guess I can stay here for a short while. But if I find any <FONT color=#a82424>clues on Rubinart,</FONT> I’ll leave right away so you better be back soon! If not, I’ll just leave this kid here all alone!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2565_grele-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2565_grele-2-a" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele${sound:npc_Grele_9817_qu_01.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>… Are you leaving now?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2565_grele-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2565_grele-3" mid="22" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Yeah, I’ll go and find Shalica under the tree. You stay right here.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2565_grele-3" image="QN_Salica.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_child_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2565_grele-3-" mid="24" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele${sound:npc_Grele_9817_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Okay. Please bring <FONT color=#086171>Lica</FONT> back.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Go to </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Undergarden</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> through Merca’s Port and find </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Shalica</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2566_salica-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2566_salica-3-a" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Shalica is staring at you from the cage. It looks like she didn’t get hurt... but then her image suddenly became fuzzy for a while.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2566_salica-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2566_salica-4" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Shalica! Are you okay? Wait a minute… This is a hologram!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2566_salica-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2566_salica-4-" mid="30" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(This looks more real than the one I saw before. Then where is Shalica...?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grugiru.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-a" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Gregory${sound:npc_Gregory_9817_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Finally! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Gregory quickly turns his head to check if anyone is around.)</FONT> There’s no one here anymore, is there? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-b" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Gosh, you scared me! What are you doing here!?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grugiru.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-c" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Gregory$<BR>I was observing the situation from afar when I saw you and I followed you here. Hah! I guess a vermin like you didn’t even realise I was on your tail. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-d" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ah... I guess he just couldn’t enter until now because of the Nest’s barrier.)</FONT><FONT color=#662500> Why did you follow me?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grugiru.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-e" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Gregory${sound:npc_Gregory_9817_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I’m here to stop you from looking for <FONT color=#086171>Miss Lica</FONT>. Thank me for saving you the trouble of finding her.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-f" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Gregory, do you know where Shalica is?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grugiru.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-4-g" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Gregory${sound:npc_Gregory_9817_qu_03.ogg}<BR>That… That I don’t know…… I’m only here because <FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT> asked me to and I just passed you his message. Go and ask <FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT> for more details. I’m going to stay here and find <FONT color=#086171>Miss Lica</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2568_grugiru-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2568_grugiru-5" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I’m going to look for Shalica too! I promised others that I’ll bring her back.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
