      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Gregory$<BR>I’m telling you your efforts will be in vain. <FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT> said it could all be part of <FONT color=#a82424>Miss Lica’s plan</FONT>. Lica should be safe so you should go back to <FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
